  "prompt": "Why do some people hate Shahrukh Khan so much?",
  "response": "As one of the most famous actors in India, Shahrukh Khan enjoys immense popularity and has a vast fan following. However, there are a few reasons why some people might dislike him:\n\n1. **Career Choices**: His film choices or acting style might not appeal to everyone. Some critics feel that he caters primarily to commercial cinema rather than taking on more artistic or experimental roles.\n\n2. **Public Image**: Shahrukh Khan's larger-than-life persona and his presence in media can be overwhelming to some. Additionally, his outspoken nature or certain public statements may rub people the wrong way.\n\n3. **Success and Jealousy**: As with any successful figure, his immense fame and fortune can breed envy and resentment among some individuals.\n\n4. **Rivalries**: Bollywood fans are often deeply loyal to their favorite actors. Shahrukh Khan might sometimes be disliked by fans of other actors due to perceived competition or rivalry.\n\n5. **Controversies**: Like many stars, Shahrukh Khan has had his share of controversies, ranging from legal issues to personal matters, which can tarnish public perception.\n\nThese reasons combined can contribute to why some individuals might hold negative opinions about him. Nonetheless, Shahrukh Khan continues to be a prominent and influential figure in the entertainment industry.",
